01:10:17.550 --> 01:10:19.740
when real refugees are coming.

01:10:19.740 --> 01:10:21.960
And they have to come very quickly.

01:10:21.960 --> 01:10:26.750
Since a lot of people were
hoping that all those --

01:10:26.750 --> 01:10:32.180
Austria 1930's was a
large anti-Semitic state

01:10:32.180 --> 01:10:34.080
and quite an oppressive state.

01:10:34.080 --> 01:10:39.020
It was not that dangerous
to live there.

01:10:39.020 --> 01:10:40.410
They would think [inaudible].

01:10:40.410 --> 01:10:45.530
But also in the crisis which ended
