01:10:49.070 --> 01:10:52.620
They were hoping to stay until the
referendum, which was scheduled

01:10:52.620 --> 01:10:54.170
to be just some days afterward.

01:10:54.170 --> 01:10:57.790
So people like Burman and others
were staying till the last moment.

01:10:57.790 --> 01:10:59.900
And then they were fleeing.

01:10:59.900 --> 01:11:04.940
One thing that I haven't mentioned
